#

Grilled Pork Tenderloin with Garlic and Herbs

40 min
$12.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

GrilledEasyHealthy

Description

A juicy and flavorful pork tenderloin, grilled to perfection with a fragrant blend of garlic and herbs.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 lb
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic cloves, minced: 4
  • fresh rosemary, chopped: 1 tbsp
  • fresh thyme, chopped: 1 tbsp
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
